Package EnchantmentOrder

Class BinaryTree

java.lang.Object
kkchengaf.EnchantmentOrder.BinaryTree
public class BinaryTree extends Object
The underlying tree structure of a search result, it stores a reference to the result data after constructor, buildTree(): Node, build the tree structure for later traversal, parseTree(inputHashMap): Integer, assign the data to all the tree nodes, traversal(node, callback): Boolean, post-order traversal and callback non leaf node
